Date: Tue, 15 Jul 2008 15:18:57 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] LTTng relay hotplug

Change relay priority so ltt heartbeat can be run _after_ relay buffer setup.

Signed-off-by: Mathieu Desnoyers <mathieu.desnoyers@polymtl.ca>
---
 kernel/relay.c |    3 +--
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/kernel/relay.c b/kernel/relay.c
index 7de644c..bdda465 100644
--- a/kernel/relay.c
+++ b/kernel/relay.c
@@ -1232,8 +1232,7 @@ EXPORT_SYMBOL_GPL(relay_file_operations);
 
 static __init int relay_init(void)
 {
-
-	hotcpu_notifier(relay_hotcpu_callback, 0);
+	hotcpu_notifier(relay_hotcpu_callback, 5);
 	return 0;
 }
 
